Setup Virtual Environment  Application:
    1. pip3 install virtualenv
    2. virtualenv venv
    3. source venv/bin/activate
    4. pip3 install -r requirements.txt

RUN Application:
    export FLASK_APP=run.py
    flask run

RUN sh file:
    | id | Operating System | Command             |
    |----|------------------|---------------------|
    | 1  |    Mac           |  sh file_name.sh    |
    | 2  |    Linux         |  ./file_name.sh     |
    | 3  |    Windows       |  bash file_name.sh  |

Docker Commands & Files:
    1. BUILD Image - build.sh
    2. Starting Container - starting.sh
    2. Stopping Container - stopping.sh
